      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7822226/" class="title-link">把知识分子拉下神坛</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7822226"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/dizhonghaideyu/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u50117252-24.jpg"></a>
