            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="31560457">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">知识分子的两个特点：1、圣化构想（预设完美来批判现实）；2、巧言令色（以文过饰非）</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2014-05-11 17:06</span>
                  
